      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car. It's been such a reliable ride and is still in really solid shape! It runs great, looks lovely, and has been well-loved and taken care of. If you're looking for something dependable that's ready for your next road trip or just the daily commute, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
