      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to a factory-spec limited-slip differential and documented rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, with recent valve adjustments and rod bearing inspections performed. Riding on staggered Style 67 alloys with fresh performance rubber, this M3 provides the visceral, high-revving analog experience enthusiasts crave.",
